These are Puzzles for 5x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: epic, family
The people have 2 different hobbies: reading, video-games
There are 2 different nationalities: nigerian, pakistani
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, cola
There are 2 different favourite colors: amber, apricot
1. the pakistani is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
2. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is reading is in an even position##4
4. the person who likes apricot is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Movie-Genre   | epic     | family     |
| Hobby   | video-games     | reading |
| Nationality   | nigerian | pakistani  |
| Beverage           | cola    | juice |
| Color         | apricot   | amber       |

