.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, mirinda
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, aconite
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, epic
There 2 different types of food: corn, broccoli
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, quad-bike
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person eating corn##1
2. the person watching action movies is the person who growsamaryllis##1
3. the person watching action movies is in an even position##4
4. the person who growsaconite is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | almond-milk |
| Flower           | aconite  | amaryllis     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic       | action      |
| Food           | corn        | broccoli      |
| Transport         | quad-bike | car     |

