.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: pink, fuchsia
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, disco
There are 2 different nationalities: japanese, mexican
2 different games are played: snooker, monopoly
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, skateboard
1. the mexican is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes fuchsia is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of disco is the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Color         | fuchsia     | pink    |
| Music-Genre           | ambient     | disco |
| Nationality   | mexican    | japanese   |
| Game         | snooker | monopoly   |
| Transport     | helicopter | skateboard |

