.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-4::.
There 2 different types of food: cranberry, kiwi
2 different pets are kept: dog, mouse
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: blues, pop
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, old-henry
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: begonia, sunflower
1. the fan of blues is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
2. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
3. the old-henry-smoker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |
| Food          | kiwi     | cranberry     |
| Pet   | dog   | mouse        |
| Music-Genre   | pop      | blues         |
| Cigar   | old-henry | swisher       |
| Flower         | begonia  | sunflower |

