House: ranch-style, tower
1. the french is the fan of country##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far right##1
3. the person who likes coral is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of country is on the right of the ranch-style house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Color      | coral      | lilac     |
| Music-Genre   | metal    | country  |
| Pet           | ferret   | hedgehog |
| Nationality         | colombian | french |
| House     | ranch-style     | tower     |

 